  "title": "Sales Assistant [Eyewear | Town Area | 5 days]",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 1055523]</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist walk-in customers with product selection and provide recommendations</li><li>Support customers in choosing suitable eyewear and conduct basic vision testing</li><li>Manage merchandising displays, restock shelves, and maintain store cleanliness</li><li>Perform cashier duties and assist with promotional campaigns</li><li>Maintain accurate customer records and provide basic follow-up support</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>At least 1 year of experience in retail sales</strong></li><li><strong>Experience in eyewear retail is an added advantage</strong></li><li>Friendly, approachable, and service-oriented personality</li><li>Able to work retail hours, including weekends and public holidays</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Felicia Chiam Kar Min<br />EA Personnel Reg. No.: R25152370<br />EA Licence No.: 07C5771 </p>",
